    <title>Hexo tutorial</title>
    <url>/2021/03/17/HexoTutorial/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="Writing-amp-Organizing-Content"><a href="#Writing-amp-Organizing-Content" class="headerlink" title="Writing &amp; Organizing Content"></a>Writing &amp; Organizing Content</h2><ul>
<li>創新md檔案至 ~/Documents/Hexo/你的資料夾名稱/source/_posts<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo new a</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
<li><p>創草稿md檔案至 ~/Documents/Hexo/你的資料夾名稱/source/_drafts</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo new draft b</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<span id="more"></span>
</li>
<li><p>在瀏覽器預覽draft檔案</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo server --draft </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>發表draft檔案，檔案也會從 ~/_draft 被移到 ~/_posts</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo publish b </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>在 ~/Documents/Hexo/你的資料夾名稱/_config.yml中<bt></p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">default_layout: post</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>改成</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">default_layout: draft</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>如此一來用 </p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo new a</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>就會預設創建草稿 (這才對吧，哪有人一new就發文ㄉ==)</p>
</li>
<li><p>除了draft跟post以外，可以創單一個page<br><br>這檔案會被存在 &lt;個人網址&gt;/aboutme</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo new page aboutme</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="Scaffolds"><a href="#Scaffolds" class="headerlink" title="Scaffolds"></a>Scaffolds</h2><ul>
<li><p>Scaffolds裡面放了三個檔案用來定義Front Matter (創建md檔時的前幾行)<br></p>
<ul>
<li>draft.md</li>
<li>page.md</li>
<li><p>post.md</p>
<p>所以說可以透過修改這些檔案讓default format有更多花樣~</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<p>以修改 ~/scaffolds/draft.md 為例<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: &#123;&#123; title &#125;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">tags:</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>可以改成<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: &#123;&#123; title &#125;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">author: Yuan</span><br><span class="line">tags:</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">## H1 TEXT</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h2 id="Tags-amp-Categories"><a href="#Tags-amp-Categories" class="headerlink" title="Tags &amp; Categories"></a>Tags &amp; Categories</h2><p>在Front Matter新增<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">tags: [tag1, tag2, tag3]</span><br><span class="line">categories:</span><br><span class="line">- [cat1, cat1.1]</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>如果tags跟categories的頁面沒出現就自己新增<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo new page tags</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo new page categories</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>接著修改<br></p>
<ol>
<li>source/tags/index.md <figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: tags</span><br><span class="line">date: 產生當下時間</span><br><span class="line">type: &quot;tags&quot;</span><br><span class="line">comments: false</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
<li>source/categories/index.md <figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: categories</span><br><span class="line">date: 產生當下時間</span><br><span class="line">type: &quot;categories&quot;</span><br><span class="line">comments: false</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ol>
<h2 id="Tag-Plugins"><a href="#Tag-Plugins" class="headerlink" title="Tag Plugins"></a>Tag Plugins</h2><p>可以用Plugins放codeblock或是iframe (youtube)之類的<br></p>
<ol>
<li>插入程式碼<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% codeblock lang:python%&#125;</span><br><span class="line">    code...</span><br><span class="line">    code...</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endcodeblock %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">add</span>(<span class="params">x, y</span>):</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> x+y</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
<li>插入youtube<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% youtube I07XMi7MHd4%&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<div class="video-container"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/I07XMi7MHd4" frameborder="0" loading="lazy" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>
</li>
</ol>
]]></content>
